esses` 从 1 跳到 2，进一步表明此 Pod 可能有异常的进程派生。\n\n3. **Checkoutservice 相关指标**:\n   - 该服务的 `rrt_max` 从正常基线 222290 跳升到 **16764476.26**，表明处理延迟极高。\n   - `Checkoutservice` 的 Pod (`checkoutservice-1`) 位于 `aiops-k8s-03` 节点，并与其资源消耗异常高度相关。\n\n4. **其他节点对比**:\n   - 在其他节点中，内存使用率最高的增长仅为约 **7%-16%**，未达到类似 `aiops-k8s-03` 的严重程度。\n\n#### 假设验证结论\n基于监控数据和异常指标分析，我们支持以下假设：\n- 假设 \"aiops-k8s-03 is the root cause due to memory exhaustion impacting checkoutservice and adservice\" 是成立的。\n- `aiops-k8s-03` 的高内存使用率直接影响了运行在该节点上的 `adservice` 和 `checkoutservice`，导致其响应变慢、错误率飙升。\n\n#### 对用户观察影响的解释\n1. Node 的内存压力直接导致 `checkoutservice` 出现高延迟。\n2. `adservice` 的资源竞争恶化，其内存和 CPU 异常升高，进而致使其错误率上升。\n3. 整体延迟和错误现象扩散至其他依赖 `checkoutservice` 和 `adservice` 的服务。\n\n### JSON 报告\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-03\",\n      \"reason\": \"Node memory usage reached 89.05%, which is the highest amongst all nodes during the fault period. This caused resource constraints for adservice and checkoutservice, leading to high response times and elevated error ratios.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"aiops-k8s-03 memory usage increased significantly (66.3% to 89.05%). Pod adservice-0 memory working set bytes surged (82487.52 to 24112345.42 bytes), indicating severe memory exhaustion.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Adservice experienced memory and client error ratio anomalies due to its hosting on the overloaded node aiops-k8s-03.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Pod adservice-0 memory increased by 292x during the fault window, coinciding with high error peaks (client_error_ratio P99 reached 6.27).\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Checkoutservice suffered from high latency (rrt_max jumped to 16764476.26), due to resource competition on the node aiops-k8s-03.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Checkoutservice-1 RRT significantly increased as aiops-k8s-03 approached memory limits. Node memory exhaustion caused delay spikes.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"}
